{"tid":138940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求解怪夢","createTime":"2017-03-01T04:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T11:44:48.000Z","uid":5984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66aeb3e18dd4d7ba015532a9f5b9e84d888ff774","tid":138940,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"發惡夢入左個連登group<br />\n同佢地出聚 果個係好多蒙面超人啲怪獸嘅世界 <br />\n但就係無蒙面超人<br />\n跟住我地遇到隻由電飯煲變成嘅怪獸<br />\n佢話佢只要仲有菌 一日都可以靠細菌增生復活<br />\n跟住好辛苦燒到佢變左一堆野 上面有啲蠟燭<br />\n所有人都準備走<br />\n跟住我返轉頭 瞬間見到果堆野變返做電飯煲 仲開始識運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我就叫啲人返去 果度係地底<br />\n一路行另一邊係酒樓<br />\n扔左個電飯煲入個煲紙檔<br />\n開始用火機係咁燒報紙檔啲野<br />\n有個巴打幫手拆開左個電飯煲<br />\n<br />\n炸左個報紙檔 本來我話賠ten thousand比個人<br />\n果個老細以為ten thousand係好多就應承左<br />\n點知有條on9以為ten thousand=one million<br />\n我好細聲同佢講 one million 係一百萬呀 唔識唔好亂講啦<br />\n比個老細聽到 佢勁開心<br />\n<br />\n果時我擔心就快爆炸 就叫啲人快啲走<br />\n跟住有啲人開始驚 因為玩到好夜<br />\n有個得中三嘅絲打仲坐左係度酒樓果啲凳喊 <br />\n跟住比啲巴打鬧佢玩到四點幾 而家先黎驚<br />\n因為就黎爆炸 我就話 我數十聲 邊個唔走 就後果自負<br />\n跟住一路數我一路走音 越黎越細聲<br />\n但個絲打聽唔到 我又要行返轉頭氹佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後無走嘅人比我踢左group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965ea2a8a35c5e375f15626896d66c2d0a29d65a","tid":138940,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"三七廿一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港九龍新界無得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc5804d75cdf7b71d3ae53c34f7333bd67da843","tid":138940,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"我想知個夢咁亂 係代表咩？<br />\n又可以代表我恐懼啲咩？"},{"pid":"e2ff3220de26dd9cb3f9c7f710e0140940ad61c1","tid":138940,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"呀joe反擊戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462d7dda80a2b0bd258e1e20c77aaf7404fdc3f4","tid":138940,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀joe反擊戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真咖me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e7d9e593bd6fdac44800335fd101d249596e77","tid":138940,"uid":27161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:44:48.000Z","msg":"好得意"}]}